{
  "stem": "268.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was actually hard physical work, but it did have a plus.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The plus was that this work was important work for the German building industry, such as they needed schools and hospitals.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we were making toilets and wash basins out of ceramic, out of clay.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "There were kilns, fired with coal, and then load into the kilns.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And then as it would burn the certain degrees, empty it out, and real hot.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we would have to have gloves, to even touch the hot contents.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And it was hard physical work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But we would get one meal a day in the factory.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And the director of the factory was a German.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "He took over the factory from-- because before there were the factory was a Jewish factory.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And, as I recall, now as I reflect and I think back of this German, he was a mean looking guy.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "He would wear-- he was a chemist by trade.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He would wear a white-- you would think he's a doctor-- a white coat, and run through the halls of the factory, because there were big long halls.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And everybody would really move, because he had a mean look.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And he was always accompanied by either a uniformed guy, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And everybody would just freeze when his steel eyes looking at you.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But, later on, as it turned out to be, the steel eyes and all this Prussian, authoritative look, was perhaps only a front.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Because deep inside, he was a good human being.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Later, into now, like 1942, when deportations began out of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "They were taking people left and right.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "He would give a special papers, stating that we are doing very important work, and we are an important labor force, and we are very much needed.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
